				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$V_{{\mathrm{RHE}}} = V_{{\mathrm{Ag}}/{\mathrm{AgCl}}} + 0.059 \times {\mathrm{pH}} + 0.197.$$\end{document}

Incident photon-to-current conversion efficiency (IPCE) values were calculated using:2IPCE%=JAcm−2⋅1240λnm⋅I(Wcm−2)⋅100%,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
